{"tid":1989762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★羅致光：3月失業綜援申請共1821宗，相對2月增加了1.5倍","createTime":"2020-04-26T08:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T11:15:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f473141f8885593f40d12fd2cb8312950b5d0ae7","tid":1989762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光今日(26日)發表網誌，指今年3月的失業綜援申請共有1821宗，相對2月的724宗已增加了1.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，政府今年6月開始透過綜援系統提供為期6個月的「失業支援計劃」，健全人士的資產上限加倍，以一個4人的健全人士住戶的限額為例，便由8.8萬港元增加一倍至17.6萬港元，自住物業暫時豁免資產審查，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一個綜援4人家庭平均可獲得每月約1.6萬港元的援助金</strong></span>。他認為，雖然不是一個很高的金額，但亦不是一般評論所指那麼低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426094729943-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200426%2Fbkn-20200426094729943-0426_00822_001.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnChYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=b8ec8faa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426094729943-0426_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"43dbf4487c623dbf83afaf8f8977a804081cd569","tid":1989762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9124af41d899a75a60b8d96bdd71ee67f3da69d","tid":1989762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"綜援4人家庭平均可獲得每月約1.6萬港元<br />\n綜援4人家庭平均可獲得每月約1.6萬港元<br />\n綜援4人家庭平均可獲得每月約1.6萬港元"},{"pid":"3823efbd5afd339d2c8fffbf542db2a1d76c4a44","tid":1989762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"disl